message.en_US: This place has certainly seen better days.
The thing we are after is located in the \c[3]basement\c[0] if I remember correctly.
There's a barrier?
[nods]
Since this place is outside of the official Playground, I can't disable it remotely.
Perhaps there is a way for you to disable it locally?\. Why don't you take a look around?
Oops!\. That doesn't look good!
Lea!\. What did you do?!
That worked!
[nods]
The device in the basement will let us \c[3]disguise\c[0] your account so that certain \c[1]blue individual\c[0] won't be able to track us.
When the original hacker was banned, all of this stuff was left abandoned.
He was only really caught because he started making trouble to other players.\. If he wasn't acting that way, he might never have been caught.
Nobody will suspect that anyone would be using this old thing, and it is quite untraceable.\. It's perfect for our situation.
Head downstairs and we can get started.\. We will be back to the playground shortly.
Looks like that opened the way.
He said there is something down there that will protect me from that flying guy from earlier.
Hopefully I can talk to him again soon, I don't know where else I can go.
You did it!
The device in the basement will let us \c[3]disguise\c[0] your account so that certain \c[1]blue individual\c[0] won't be able to track us.
When the original hacker was banned, all of this stuff was left abandoned.
He was only really caught because he started making trouble to other players.\. If he wasn't acting that way, he might never have been caught.
Nobody will suspect that anyone would be using this old thing, and it is quite untraceable.\. It's perfect for our situation.
Head downstairs and we can get started.\. We will be back to the playground shortly.
[nods]
What is going on?!!
WHO WOULD DESIGN THIS?!
Please be careful, there are no security protocols enforced out here.
Be careful Lea!\. We don't know what this will do!
What?!\! Impossible!
I'm losing my conne....\......Le...\....?...
HI?!?
..............\!what is even happening to me...
WAIT!\! I CAN TALK NOW?
What a relief.\. I was starting to go crazy.
Hi!\. Can you hear me?
...Hello?
I guess that machine also severed his connection.
I wonder if his connection is what causes the speech problems in the first place?
Just great..\. I'm all alone in the middle of nowhere and there is a crazy flying wierdo hunting me.
I should probably find the way to the \c[3]basement\c[0].
This place sure is pretty nasty, just how long has it been abandoned?
What was that?
Hello again!
When you activated that program, I ran into abnormal network interference.
But I managed to get it working again!
[nods]
There has to be a way past that barrier somehow in here.
Just be careful with this old equipment!
Oh! It looks like you managed to turn off the barrier!
[nods]
Well done! Now please head downstairs so we can continue.
